Study.Protocol: The participant stands upright with hands on hips, bends the knees, and jumps maximally with full leg extension. Three trials are performed with adequate rest between jumps.

Description.en: Measures vertical jump height using a countermovement jump. The best of three trials is typically used for analysis.
Description.de: Misst die vertikale Sprunghöhe mittels Countermovement Jump. In der Regel wird der Bestwert aus drei Versuchen für die Analyse verwendet.
